content: twilwa: Merged 3 PRs this week, including a significant feature PR (#2417) adding a workflow to block minified JS (+816/-146 lines) and a refactoring effort to dockerize smoke tests (#2420, +283/-151 lines), which was later reverted (#2459). Contributed substantial code changes across 39 files (+5494/-215 lines) with a focus on tests and configuration files, while also providing 3 approving reviews for other contributors' work.
